infos.text: Rider-class Servant, Altria Pendragon.

[r]
Now that I'm here, brace yourself to begin living your life properly!

[r]
There will be no more going back to sleep once your alarm goes off, and no more letting yourself get out of shape. I will clean everything! I will do the laundry!

[r]
C-cooking... Well, I'll do my best...
Oh my, you are a rather cute Master!
I am Gilles de Rais, and I have come to you at your invitation.[r]
From here on, I shall be at your command.
I will always be there for you![sr]Your reliable Shrine Maiden Fox, Caster, has now arrived!
Hello to the wonderful you.[r]Lets make this a beautiful dream.

I am a third-rate servant, Andersen.[r]
Just throw me in the corner of a bookshelf.
I am Caster-class Shakespeare, and I have come to see you!
[r]So, shall we begin our story?
Greetings, Master of Chaldea.

[r]
I am Merlin.
People call me the Mage of Flowers.

[r]
Just call me Merlin.
I don't care for formalities.

Nice to meet you once again.[r]
I am Servant Leonardo Da Vinci.[r]
Yes, from now on, I will be Da Vinci-chan only for you!

infos.text: I have been summoned upon your request.[r]Please, be friends with me, Paracelsus.

My name is Steam King.[r]
I died once and now my existence lives along in the imaginary world.

Servant, Caster.[r]
Reincarnation of the Sky God Horus, I, Nitocris have answered your summons.

[r]
As you can see, I am a pharaoh, but vastly inexperienced.

[r]
Thus, for now I shall accept you as my ally.

[r]
However, I have one thing to say.
Bow your head. You're being disrespectful!
Ahh, looks like you hit the jackpot, Master?
[r]I am the Devil, Mephistopheles. And I have been called upon.
I am Amadeus Wolfgang Mozart!

[r]
Leave battles aside, I promise only to decorate your life!
Servant, Caster.
[r]...It is easier to understand if I say Geronimo, right?
I'm Medea, a Caster-class Servant.[r]I look forward to working with you.
Caster, Gilgamesh.

[r]
I have materialized in this form to meet Uruk's time of need,
not in response to your summon.

[r]
Dont get cocky, mongrel.
I am Servant Zhuge Liang...What? You are asking if I am the wrong person?

[r]
Exactly, I am actually El-Melloi the Second.[r]But I did inherit all the powers, so there's no issue there.
I am from the Holy Grail. The one serving as the terminal of the Holy Grail.

[r]
A temporary form. A temporary Servant.

[r]
My name... Please call me Irisviel.
Oops! I guess this time I am materialized as a Caster?[r]
Oh, its you guys! We met before right?
My name is Xuanzang Sanzang!
Through the guidance of the Buddha, I have arrived!
[r]Umm, I am a Caster!
...It's all right.
[r]This Caster will guide you along the way!
Servant, Caster.
[r]I am Thomas Alva Edison!
[r]Don't worry about my looks!
This is the symbol of America!
Trick or treat!
There's no need for introductions, right?
[sr]Demoness Elisabeth Bthory.
[sr]In response to your passionate support,
I have been summoned in my best dress!

infos.text: So I have been Summoned.

[r]
...My name is Scheherazade.

[r]
If you would hear my one simple wish...

[r]
It would be for me to serve you as my king, forever.
So I have been summoned.

[r]
...I am...for now...the Caster of the Nightless City.
There may be a time when I can reveal my True Name...
Or rather, when the time comes, I will have to do so in order to not die.
Surprised by the sudden swimsuit? I bet you're surprised!

[r]
Umu, I am ecstatic too! My heart is racing!

[r]
Caster, Nero Claudius, here to answer your summon!

[r]
Let's make this an unforgettable summer!

infos.text: Hey! Now that I'm here, you won't have to be lonely anymore.[r]
That's because you summoned me, the witch, Circe![r]
Teehee.
I'm the Caster of Okeanos.[r]
Now that I'm here, you won't have to be lonely anymore.[r]
That's because you summoned me, the Falcon Witch![r]
Teehee.

infos.text: Hello, I'm here![r]
I'm the queen who governed the nation of Sheba.[r]
Please call me Sheba.[r]
Yes?
My real name?[r]
Hmmm... Well, I'm afraid that will cost you.
Hellooo, I'm here![r]
Just call me Caster of Midrash for now.[r]
I'll be a big help!
I am Sasaki Kojirou, an Assassin-class Servant.[r]And I have been called upon to your service.
Assassin-class Servant. I heard your call from the shadows.
Now that you have command over the army of shadows, victory is at hand.

[r]
You can rest easy now, Master.
Assassin Jack the Ripper[r]Nice to meet you, Mother.
My name is Jekyll. [r]I am...different from Hyde.
Hah, did you think I would appear from within a rolled-up carpet?
...Well, perhaps I considered it,
but rejected the idea since this is our first meeting.

[r]
I am the last Pharaoh, Cleopatra VII Philopator.

[r]
Master,
could you please refrain from holding your head higher than the sun?
Everything, everything, everything as you would will it.
[r]I will offer all of myself to you.
This body, this heart, all of it...
Haha. Trying to summon a goddess to this world, such an interesting and poor soul.[r]You, what is your name?
My name is Jing Ke, an Assassin-class Servant.
[r]I do feel complicated for being summoned after that failure.[r]But let's plan well next time!
My name is Charles-Henri Sanson.[r]I have been summoned and come at your request!
Whoever sees my face will learn the meaning of fear...including you.
Assassin-class Servant.[r]I go by the name of Mata Hari. Nice to meet you.
More dirty work huh... Doesn't matter, happens all the time.

Ah. I guess this must be fate.[r]
Please call me Carmilla. I am an Assassin-class Servant.
...The code name is Heroine X.

[r]
I am a Servant summoned in response to the recent social problems involving an increasing number of Sabers.
It is nice to meet you.
Servant, Assassin.
Fuuma Kotarou.
I might look like this, but please don't let that bother you...
Assassin, Shuten-Douji.

[r]
Fufu. Please accept my gratitude for summoning me.

[r]
I will do as I please but...
you don't mind, do you?
Assassin-class Servant.
Name's Ryougi Shiki.

[r]
...Does this work as a greeting?
I guess it is a weird one huh...

[r]
I am a bit different, but I will beat the crap out of our enemies.
Is it your first time in a haunted house?
It's pretty common in any populated city...

[r]
Well, follow me as far as you can without dying.

[r]
Assassin-class.

[r]
Please, give me your orders.
Assassin of Paraso, here to heed your call.

[r]
I vow loyalty to my new Lord Master.

[r]
Excuse me for using an alias instead of my True Name.

[r]
I am prepared to accept any type of punishment.
Katou Danzo, online.

[r]
Your input, please, Master.

[r]
As I am a shinobi, I will obey any order.
Uh...um?
Yes, yes, I'm Osakabehime, Assassin.

[r]
So...um, can I go home now?
I can't?
Fiiine.
[image berserker_language_1]
Shuhuhuhuhuhuhuhuhu...
[image berserker_language_1]
...Uhhhhhhhhhh.

[r]Let's go beat them up, Master.
[r]...Hey hey, don't back off now.
Whoooo!!
My... Action... Is... My... Destiny...

Please rest assured now that I'm here.
[r]Let's save everyone's lives.

Uraaaaaaaaaaaaa!

[r]...My color has nothing to do with you.

the leader of the oni clan on Mt. Ooe.
Hello, my dear Mage.

[r]

Oh dear.

[r]
Erm...I am Minamoto-no-Raikou.

[r]I am sure it's only a coincidence.

No matter my appearance, I am still me![r]
Without fail, I shall save the world with you.

But if you wanted a detective or an investigator, you drew the right card.

[r]
I'd really rather not, but I suppose I'll form a contract with you. You should be honored, okay?

[r]
I have come to answer the voices calling for salvation.

[r]
But...hehe...

[r]
I wonder about the sort of person who would summon a woman like me.

[r]
I am the Devilish Bodhisattva who savors all living creatures, sentient or not.

You have no choice now but to stay with me until the very end.
I am Alter Ego Magus Aegis Elisabeth Channel.

[r]
I apologize for the trouble I caused you...and that Elisabeth continues ceaselessly
causing for you.

Elisabeth Channel II.

[r]

Hey there!

[r]

I responded immediately when I heard your call!

The reincarnation of vengence itself?
[r]Well precisely, I am the grudge of darkness

[r]
...What's with that look?
Come on, here's the contract.
...Hmph.

[r]
Use me well.
I shall use you well, too.

[r]
Whose untimely end will be displayed first?
It should be something to see.

[image berserker_language_3]

but take good care of me, little Master!
